query: UPDATE member SET name = COALESCE(?1, name), phone = COALESCE(?2, phone), card_number = COALESCE(?3, card_number), marketing_group_id = COALESCE(?4, marketing_group_id), birthday = COALESCE(?5, birthday), notes = COALESCE(?6, notes), is_active = COALESCE(?7, is_active), updated_at = ?8 WHERE id = ?9
